Architecture Diagram Overview:
1. [Farm Environment] 
(Aquaponics, Aeroponics, Drip Irrigation)

2. [Integrated Systems]
(Water Quality, Nutrient Delivery, Water flow)

3. [Sensor Network & Data Collection] 
(Soil Moisture, Nutrient Levels, Environmental Sensors, Cameras)


4. [Edge Devices & Data Pre-processing]   
(Arduino or Raspberry Pi)
       
5. [ML Model & Predictive Analytics] 
(Data Collection, Data Cleaning, Model Training, Predictions)

6. [Control Systems] 
(Automated Irrigation, Nutrient Management) 
                                                  
7. [User Interface]
(Mobile App, Web Dashboard)  
